
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# <type>(<scope>)!: <description>          max 72 chars, ideally ≤50
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   feat      new feature                            → MINOR bump
#   fix       bug fix                                → PATCH bump
#   perf      performance improvement
#   refactor  restructure, no behavior change
#   style     formatting only, no logic change
#   test      add or fix tests
#   docs      documentation only
#   build     build system / dependencies
#   ci        CI/CD configuration
#   chore     housekeeping / misc
#   revert    revert a previous commit
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   scope     optional area: (auth) (api) (ui) (db) — project-specific
#   !         breaking change → MAJOR bump
#
#   subject   imperative mood · no capital · no trailing period
#   body      explain WHY, not what · wrap at 72 chars (leave blank line above)
#   footer    BREAKING CHANGE: … · Closes #id · Signed-off-by: Name <email>
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
